@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos((0.79 * wp.abs(tmp + 0.69)))
    v1 = (((v2 + 0.43 / v1 + 0.50) + (v0 + 0.38 / v2 + 0.31)) / (wp.abs(v2 + 0.85) + (v0 + 0.42 - tmp + 0.52)))
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v1 + 0.04)) + v2)
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.24)) / wp.sin((v1 + 0.08 + v1 + 0.12)))
    tmp = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.51 + v0 + 0.64)) / ((v2 + 0.45 / v1 + 0.26) * (tmp + 0.48 * tmp + 0.18)))
    data[tid] = v0
